OL,3,C'If this place was open he would still
OL,4,Cbe alive': Fight to save boxing club
OL,6,FGranada Reports Sports Correspondent
OL,7,FMike Hall has been to speaking to
OL,8,Fpeople on the Darnhill Estate in
OL,9,FHeywood about the importance of re-
OL,10,Fopening the boxing gym
OL,12,FA boxing gym destroyed by fire is
OL,13,Ffighting to secure funding to re-open
OL,14,F- claiming had it been able to it
OL,15,Fcould have saved the life of a young
OL,16,Fboy.
OL,18,FDarnhill and Heywood Amateur Boxing
OL,19,FClub closed after the blaze ripped
OL,20,Fthrough the community hub 10 years ago.
