OL,3,C'If this place was open he would still
OL,4,Cbe alive': Fight to save boxing club
OL,6,FBut despite the strong desire for a
OL,7,Fcentre - which had been in place for
OL,8,Fmore than 60 years - construction of a
OL,9,Fnew gym has stalled due to a cash
OL,10,Fshortage, leaving the town's aspiring
OL,11,Fyoung boxers forced to train in the
OL,12,Fcar park, often in the rain.
OL,14,FThe community has been rocked even
OL,15,Ffurther after aspiring young fighter
OL,16,FHarvey Greenhalgh took his own life -
OL,17,Fsomething his coach claims might have
OL,18,Fbeen prevented had he had a centre to
OL,19,Ftrain at.
