OL,3,C'If this place was open he would still
OL,4,Cbe alive': Fight to save boxing club
OL,6,FHarvey, 16, had grown in confidence
OL,7,Fduring a summer boxing camp in the
OL,8,Ftown.
OL,10,F"It's shocked the community and his
OL,11,Ffamily to the core," Dale Gaucas,
OL,12,FChairman of Darnhill and Heywood Self
OL,13,FDevelopment Centre, said.
OL,15,F"Myself, the grief, the guilt, the
OL,16,Fpain, if this place had been open that
OL,17,Fboy would still be with us.
OL,19,F"I truly believe that. It's a place to
OL,20,Fcome isn't it?
