OL,6,F"Even when I was a kid, you don't
OL,7,Falways go home to mum and tell them
OL,8,Fyour problems, or your mates. You go
OL,9,Fto your coaches and mentors."
OL,11,FDale said the community has also
OL,12,Fsuffered recently with the loss of
OL,13,Fimportant services.
OL,15,F"It's had two public houses knocked
OL,16,Fdown, a school knocked down, a church
OL,17,Fknocked down," he said.
