OL,6,F"What that does is take the heart out
OL,7,Fof the community. For the youth they
OL,8,Fhave no place to call home after
OL,9,Fschool, where do they go?
OL,11,F"This community is in the lowest 3%
OL,12,Fdeprived areas in the country, the
OL,13,Flowest percentage in crime, in
OL,14,Feducation, in opportunities outside
OL,15,Fthe home, in physical and mental
OL,16,Fhealth.
OL,18,F"If we don't solve this problem now,
OL,19,Fit'll stay like this forever."
