OL,3,C'If this place was open he would still
OL,4,Cbe alive': Fight to save boxing club
OL,6,FThe plan is to build not just a boxing
OL,7,Fgym but a self development centre that
OL,8,Fwould include employment and education
OL,9,Fopportunities as well as an aerobics
OL,10,Fand fitness area.
OL,12,FAround #300,000 has been raised so far
OL,13,Fthrough grants and fundraising, which
OL,14,Fhas provided the basic building, but
OL,15,Fanother #300,000 is needed to complete
OL,16,Fthe project.
OL,18,FThe community says Harvey's death has
OL,19,Fonly strengthened resolve to complete
OL,20,Ftheir goal - with fundraising
OL,21,Fcontinuing in his name.
