OL,3,C'If this place was open he would still
OL,4,Cbe alive': Fight to save boxing club
OL,6,FThe children participating in the
OL,7,Fsessions say the centre is a much-
OL,8,Fneeded addition to their community.
OL,10,F"There's not really anything to do,
OL,11,Fbecause everyone is just messing about
OL,12,Fdoing naughty stuff. If that was there
OL,13,Fwe'd have more stuff to do and be in
OL,14,Fbetter shape," one said.
OL,16,FWhile another added: "I really want it
OL,17,Fto be finished because a lot of older
OL,18,Fpeople get to do boxing but younger
OL,19,Fkids on this estate don't get chance
OL,20,Fto."
