OL,6,FLocal residents are also giving their
OL,7,Ffull backing to the fundraising
OL,8,Fproject, Jenny Kennedy said: "I'm 73
OL,9,Fthis year, so last year I did a
OL,10,Fbirthday request and I got #1,200 in
OL,11,Fbirthday gifts and it was donated to
OL,12,Fthe boxing.
OL,14,F"And I've done it again this year."
